<p style='margin-left:20px;'>
<input type="radio" name="employer_tuition" value=0> No</p>

<p>Are you also applying to other programs? </p>
<p style='margin-left:20px;'>
<input type="radio" name="other_program_apps" value=1> Yes</p>
<p style='margin-left:20px;'>
